    <string name="profile_how_it_works_title">How It Works</string>
    <string name="profile_how_it_works_intro">FlowLedger keeps the app simple for day-to-day use while still showing useful finance signals.</string>
    <string name="profile_how_it_works_step_1">1. Add income in the original currency you received it in.</string>
    <string name="profile_how_it_works_step_2">2. Add expenses once, or set them as monthly or yearly if they repeat.</string>
    <string name="profile_how_it_works_step_3">3. The app stores values in a normalized form, then shows them in your preferred display currency.</string>
    <string name="profile_how_it_works_step_4">4. Dashboard charts focus on the key visuals: income mix, spending split, what is spent, and what is left.</string>
    <string name="profile_how_it_works_step_5">5. Recent History collects the descriptive notes, recurring updates, and transaction record changes in one separate place.</string>
